data.description: Welcome to this adorable home centrally located. offers an open concept floor plan with two living areas, spacious bedrooms (4), and Three full bathrooms which are rare to find. Wrap around garage with a huge fenced backyard with plenty of room for your tools and storage necessities. The Home also comes pre-wired for a generator. This home will need a little TLC. Call your local agent to view this home today!
